      <para styleclass="Heading3">Conditions to Turn On Signal Lamp</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">Each signal lamp is turned on in the following conditions.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text style="font-weight:bold;">Signal Lamp 1 (Red), Buzzer (Option)</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
