      <li styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:4px; margin-left:13px;"> End of Program (M02, M30)</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="margin-left:13px;"> Program Stop (M00, M01)</li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:4px; margin-left:13px;"></para>
